Most frameworks fail all four.
+-----------------------------------------------------------------+
|                    FAILURE MATRIX OF OPEN MODELS                |
+-------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| Condition         | Primary Violation Mechanism                 |
+-------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| 1. Closure        | Runaway divergence, numerical spillover,    |
|                   | need for external manual clipping.          |
| 2. Completeness   | Unmodeled environmental noise, exogenous    |
|                   | forcing functions, hidden state parameters. |
| 3. Causality      | Descriptive curve-fitting, correlation      |
|                   | without an underlying mechanical generator M|
| 4. Consistency    | Non-stationarity, parameter drift, manual   |
|                   | retuning across temporal updates.           |
+-------------------+---------------------------------------------+
Reality satisfies all four.
